\v 17 Ungafisi indlu kamakhelwane wakho, ungafisi umkamakhelwane wakho, lenceku yakhe, lencekukazi yakhe, lenkabi yakhe, lobabhemi wakhe, njalo loba yini ekamakhelwane wakho\x + Roma 7.7; 13.9.\x*.
\s Ukwesaba kwabantu
\p
\v 18 Bonke abantu basebebona imidumo\x + Heb. 12.18.\x* lemibane lelizwi lophondo\x + Gen. 15.17. Dute. 4.12.\x*, lentaba ithunqa\x + 19.18.\x*. Kwathi abantu bekubona bathuthumela, bema khatshana;
\v 19 bathi kuMozisi: Khuluma wena lathi, njalo sizakuzwa\x + Dute. 5.27; 18.16. Gal. 3.19,20. Heb. 12.19.\x*; kodwa uNkulunkulu kangakhulumi lathi hlezi sife\x + Dute. 5.25.\x*.
\v 20 UMozisi wasesithi ebantwini: Lingesabi\x + 1 Sam. 12.20. Isa. 41.10,13.\x*; ngoba uNkulunkulu ufikile ukuze alilinge\x + Gen. 22.1. Dute. 13.3.\x*, lokuze ukwesabeka kwakhe kube phambi kwenu\x + Dute. 4.10; 6.2; 10.12; 17.19; 28.58. Zaga 3.7; 16.6. Isa. 8.13.\x*, ukuze lingoni.
\v 21 Abantu bema-ke khatshana; kodwa uMozisi wasondela emnyameni onzima lapho uNkulunkulu ayekhona\x + Dute. 4.11. 1 Kho. 8.12. 2 Sam. 22.10. Hlab. 18.9; 97.2.\x*.
\s Umthetho omayelana lelathi
\p
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Uzakutsho njalo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli \add uthi\add*: Lina selibonile ukuthi ngikhulume lani ngisemazulwini\x + Dute. 4.36. Neh. 9.13.\x*.
\v 23 Kaliyikwenza kanye lami onkulunkulu besiliva, njalo onkulunkulu begolide kaliyikuzenzela\x + 32.31. 2 Kho. 17.33. Hez. 20.39. Zef. 1.5.\x*.
\v 24 Ngenzela ilathi lenhlabathi, unikele phezu kwalo iminikelo yakho yokutshiswa leminikelo yakho yokuthula, izimvu zakho lenkabi zakho. Kuyo yonke indawo lapho engilenza ibizo lami ukuthi likhunjulwe khona\x + Dute. 12.5,11,21; 14.23; 16.6,11; 26.2. 1 Kho. 8.43; 9.3. 2 Lan. 6.6; 7.16; 12.13. Ezra 6.12. Neh. 1.9. Hlab. 74.7. Jer. 7.10,12.\x* ngizakuza kuwe ngikubusise\x + Gen. 12.2. Dute. 7.13.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa uba ungenzela ilathi lamatshe\x + Dute. 27.5. Josh. 8.31.\x*, awuyikulakha \add ngamatshe\add* abaziweyo\x + 1 Kho. 5.17. 1 Lan. 22. 2.\x*; ngoba nxa uphakamisela kulo insimbi yakho yokubaza\x + 2 Kho. 5.11.\x*, uyalingcolisa.
\v 26 Awuyikukhwela phezu kwelathi lami ngezikhwelo, ukuze ubunqunu bakho bungembulwa phezu kwalo.